    </p>
    <p>
      Features include:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>2D and 3D views for building design</li>
      <li>Phase-based construction planning (Existing/Demolition/New)</li>
      <li>Bill of Materials (BOM) generation</li>
      <li>Business suite for quotes, invoices, and customer management</li>
      <li>Multi-discipline support (electrical, plumbing, drywall, ceilings)</li>
      <li>Italian and English localization</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
